<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I tried to get an instance of Zend_Mime_Message via its createFromMessage() method but I am getting an E_WARNING (see. below). I tried to find out what it is causing it and found out, that an array instead of a string will be put as parameter to Zend_Mime_Part's constructor. You have to use $part['body'] instead of $part as parameter for Zend_Mime_Part::__construct().</p>

<p>{quote}Notice: Array to string conversion in /usr/share/php/Zend/Mime.php on line 131{quote}</p>

